HEADWORD: Petroglyphy
<hw>Pe*trog"ly*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Petro</ets> + Gr. <grk>gly`fein</grk> to carve.]</ety>
